snippet.title: Starbot: ASVERTICHAOS Demo - TRAILER
snippet.description:
Find the game on Itch.io, Gamejolt and SAGE 2024!

Trailer made by  @amuamisinderio494 and @ug32t52 

In the continent of Asvertica, Stell plans to spend the afternoon camping with his friends, Tina and Nile.
But, when Tina disappears, it's up to Stell Starbot and Nile to find her!

STARBOT - ASVERTICHAOS is a fast-paced 2D platformer focused on fluid movement. Explore the continent of Asvertica and uncover its secrets as you explore every crack and crevice while meeting a wacky set of characters to find your friend!

-FOLLOW US-
Twitter: https://x.com/Asvertichaos

Discord: https://discord.gg/p59sK8SkPs
